# Changelog

## 1.0.1 (2026-05-30)

- Fix Cursor CLI install under `/opt/cursor-agent` so the `cloudron` user can run `agent`
- Bootstrap agent binary to `/app/data` on start for older image layouts
- Fix git operations to use `HOME=/app/data` (avoids read-only `/home/cloudron`)
- Admin connect: wait for device-flow URL and poll `/admin/connect/status`
- Report API key auth as authenticated in connect status without calling `agent status`

## 1.0.0 (2026-05-29)

- Initial release
- My Machines worker (`agent worker start`)
- Admin UI with browser sign-in and API key fallback
- Fat image: Cursor CLI, Node 20, Playwright/Chromium, build tools
- Community distribution via CloudronVersions.json and GHCR images
